# Drop editor/notes markdown at the repo root but keep template + source
# markdown. `dist/templates/**/prompts/*.system.md` ship in the npm tarball
# and must land in the Docker image too. So we exclude root-level .md and
# then re-include the paths that need to build.
*.md
!README.md
!packages/**/*.md
!scripts/**/*.md
